### HBRS Campus-Messenger
The messenger works with an LDAP login and can be used to create chats with 2 - n different users. 

You can find the component [here](http://www2.inf.fh-bonn-rhein-sieg.de/~mgiese2s/webeng/phase4/).

### Authors and Contributors
The author of this project is @MarcoGiesen and a useful contributor was @FranzD1991 who helped in testing.
